title: Teppo Salmisaari
text: Teppo Salmisaari (June 19, 1924, <a href="Tampere">Tampere</a> - July 9, 2006) was a <a href="Finland">Finnish</a> <a href="canoe%20racing">sprint canoer</a> who competed in the early 1950s. He finished ninth in the <a href="Canoeing%20at%20the%201952%20Summer%20Olympics%20%E2%80%93%20Men%27s%20C-2%2010000%20metres">C-2 10000 m</a> event at the <a href="1952%20Summer%20Olympics">1952 Summer Olympics</a> in <a href="Helsinki">Helsinki</a>.
